			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>Bella Nanny Associates Inc,</strong>&nbsp;is a premier nanny and household staffing agency with one simple mission: To support and help busy families find a nurturing and honest childcare specialist, whose qualifications, passion and experience exceeds expectations. &nbsp;We are looking for experienced, professional nannies that are dedicated to their profession and have a passion for caring for children. &nbsp;</p>
<p>
Bella Nanny Associates assists families by providing personalized service designed to meet their special needs. &nbsp;Our Nanny and domestic staff candidates represent the highest standards in character, commitment, and service. We serve many happy families throughout Chicagoland. &nbsp;We are looking for individuals who are honest, caring, and loving to be considered for our current openings. &nbsp;</p>
<p>
We care about the needs of our candidates and seek to assist in fostering the advancement of their careers. &nbsp;We offer all nannies ongoing support throughout the placement process. &nbsp;Our service is free of charge to all prospective BNA candidates.</p>
